      <title>美国称胡塞武装袭击了沙特船只，但巴赫里称并非目标</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-03/us-says-houthis-hit-saudi-ship-but-bahri-says-wasn-t-targeted</link>
