    <item>
      <title>EFG 的 Murray 表示，对利率的期望需谨慎</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-09-03/careful-what-you-wish-for-on-rates-efg-s-murray-says-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[EFG 资产管理公司副首席投资官 Daniel Murray 表示，市场应该“谨慎对待”美联储利率，因为降息步伐加快意味着宏观环境减弱，“这通常对股市不利”。他在彭博电视台发表了讲话。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-09-03/careful-what-you-wish-for-on-rates-efg-s-murray-says-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 03 Sep 2024 08:22:10 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>帕特拉称印度需要十年更快的增长才能实现目标</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-03/india-needs-faster-growth-for-a-decade-to-meet-goals-patra-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[印度央行一位高级官员表示，印度需要十年的快速经济增长才能实现总理纳伦德拉·莫迪提出的到 2047 年成为发达国家的目标。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-03/india-needs-faster-growth-for-a-decade-to-meet-goals-patra-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 03 Sep 2024 08:18:34 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Illumina 和 Grail 诉讼案败诉，欧盟合并权受挫</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-03/illumina-grail-deal-was-wrongly-probed-by-eu-top-court-rules</link>
      <description><![CDATA[根据最高法院的一项裁决，欧盟本不应调查 Illumina Inc. 放弃以 70 亿美元收购癌症检测提供商 Grail Inc. 的交易，这一裁决对欧盟审查更多全球交易的努力造成了重大打击。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-03/illumina-grail-deal-was-wrongly-probed-by-eu-top-court-rules</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 03 Sep 2024 07:48:06 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
